com.enremmeta.rtb

Class BidInFlightInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enremmeta.rtb.BidInFlightInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Jsonable, Serializable

    public final class BidInFlightInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable, Jsonable
    Encapsulates information about a bid in flight - which may be lost or won, and the lost or won (or assumed lost) information may be handled on a different machine. To be used in LostAuctionTask.
    Author:
    Gregory Golberg (grisha@alum.mit.edu)
